 error message and <see cref="System.Exception.InnerException"/>
				<see langword=" "/> property.</para>
		</summary>
		<param name="message">The message to display to the client when the exception is thrown.</param>
		<param name=" inner">The <see cref="System.Exception.InnerException"/> , if any, that threw the current exception.</param>
	</doc><doc for="ConfigurationException.ConfigurationException6">
		<summary>
			<para>Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="System.Configuration.ConfigurationException"/> with the specified error
