		</summary>
		<param name="message">The message to display to the client when the exception is thrown.</param>
		<param name=" node">The <see cref="System.Xml.XmlNode"/> that contains the error.</param>
		<remarks>
			<para> A constructor that accepts an <see cref="System.Xml.XmlNode"/> 
argument should always be used when reporting errors
thrown by configuration section handlers.</para>
		</remarks>
	</doc><doc for="ConfigurationException.ConfigurationException4">
		<summary>
			<para>Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="System.Configuration.ConfigurationException"/> class with the
