		</summary>
		<param name="message">The message to display to the client when the exception is thrown.</param>
		<param name=" inner">The <see cref="System.Exception.InnerException"/> , if any, that threw the current exception.</param>
		<param name=" node">The <see cref="System.Xml.XmlNode"/> that contains the error.</param>
		<remarks>
			<para>A constructor that accepts an <see cref="System.Xml.XmlNode"/>
argument should always be used when
reporting errors from configuration section handlers.</para>
		</remarks>
