		</summary>
		<value>
			<para>The file name and line number of the error.</para>
		</value>
		<remarks>
			<para>To get the base error message without file name and line number information, use
      the <see cref="System.Configuration.ConfigurationException.BareMessage"/> property.</para>
		</remarks>
	</doc><doc for="ConfigurationException.BareMessage">
		<summary>
			<para>Gets the base error message without file name and line number information.</para>
		</summary>
		<value>
			<para>The base error message.</para>
		</value>
		<remarks>
			<para>To get the error message with file name and line number information, use the
